2026-05-11T07:42:27.1741791Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1742562Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1743247Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1744096Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1744927Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1745755Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1746572Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1747407Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1748225Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1748994Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1749595Z 33    -->
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1750214Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1781807Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1783172Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1784191Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
