2026-05-11T07:42:27.1791606Z 38        Used on Samsung and other OEM devices that aggressively optimize
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1792553Z 39        battery usage. MainActivity shows a one-time dialog that opens
2026-05-11T07:42:27.1793474Z 40        the system "ignore battery optimizations" screen so scheduled
